12
00:01:24,818 --> 00:01:26,419
I'm frustrated too.

13
00:01:27,620 --> 00:01:29,689
I'm confused like crazy.

14
00:01:30,657 --> 00:01:32,859
I don't know what's wrong with my head.

15
00:01:33,226 --> 00:01:35,061
