The fish his father left behind died.

38
00:03:21,167 --> 00:03:23,536
He was feeling all emotional,

39
00:03:23,603 --> 00:03:25,038
and I happened to be there.

40
00:03:26,673 --> 00:03:30,176
That's why he made such a mistake.

41
00:03:30,310 --> 00:03:34,214
Still, would you expect your boss
to do that to just any girl?

42
00:03:35,448 --> 00:03:36,616
Don't you know?

43
00:03:36,950 --> 00:03:40,353
The woman he loves is Veronica Park.

44
00:03:40,587 --> 00:03:42,622
She's you after all.

45
00:03:46,826 --> 00:03:48,394
She has money.

46
