because she has a lot of money.

47
00:03:51,397 --> 00:03:54,400
Also because she is competent
and comes from a prestigious family.

48
00:03:55,668 --> 00:03:57,103
She's not me.

49
00:03:58,171 --> 00:03:59,372
Never.

50
00:04:03,476 --> 00:04:04,944
I'm sorry.

51
00:04:06,613 --> 00:04:08,681
