lose the ability to recognize faces.

64
00:05:13,713 --> 00:05:16,215
I also lost the ability
to control my emotions and desires.

65
00:05:16,349 --> 00:05:18,384
I'm sure that's it.

66
00:05:18,451 --> 00:05:19,819
What are you talking about?

67
00:05:20,186 --> 00:05:21,421
The thing is,

68
00:05:22,355 --> 00:05:26,125
I'm in love with two women
at the same time.

69
00:05:28,728 --> 00:05:32,198
What's with you? Have you lost your mind?

70
00:05:32,365 --> 00:05:33,800
Right? I'm living

71
00:05:33,866 --> 00:05:35,702
in a civilized, monogamous society.

72
00:05:35,835 --> 00:05:39,172
