in my life.

73
00:05:39,872 --> 00:05:42,008
And here I'm having these crazy thoughts.

74
00:05:43,276 --> 00:05:44,577
Do a CT scan right now.

75
00:05:44,677 --> 00:05:46,479
There's something wrong with me.

76
00:05:48,815 --> 00:05:50,983
Seeing you like this reminds me

77
00:05:51,417 --> 00:05:54,320
of back when I had to choose my specialty.

78
00:05:54,420 --> 00:05:56,289
I was torn between

79
